The Saint Louis Rapid & Blitz, part of the Grand Chess Tour, takes place from November 14-18 at the Saint Louis Chess Club, Missouri, USA.

The 10-player event consists of a Rapid round-robin and a Blitz double round-robin, under time controls of 25 minutes for the entire game and a 10-second increment (Rapid), and 5 minutes for the entire game and a 2-second increment (Blitz. Points scored in rapid count as double in the overall standings. The total prize fund is $175,000. Official website: grandchesstour.org
